Analysis of the Bulgarian division of Re/Max.
Bulgaria, with its cheap ski apartments and houses on the seashore, is now the most sought-after Eastern European objective of real estate purchases.
The most of the mountains are in the course of Bansko, Borovec, Pamprovo and Vitosha, on the sea coast then Albena, Golden Sands, Sunny Coast, the ancient cities of Sozopol and Nesebar, but more and more people are also looking for properties around Kavarna and Balčik.
